## CLI Quick Reference

### Session Commands

```bash
# Start/resume session
./workflow session --agent {{ agent_id }}

# Check session status
./workflow status
```

### Logging Commands

```bash
# Record a decision
./workflow decision --title "Decision Title" --rationale "Why this decision was made"

# Record an assumption
./workflow assumption --title "Assumption Title" --reasoning "Basis for assumption"

# Track artifact update
./workflow artifact --file "filename.md" --action "created|updated"
```

### Handoff Commands

{% if next_agent_id %}
```bash
# Handoff to next agent
./workflow handoff --from {{ agent_id }} --to {{ next_agent_id }} --artifacts "{{ required_artifacts | join(', ') if required_artifacts else 'artifact1.md, artifact2.md' }}"
```
{% else %}
```bash
# End workflow (terminal agent)
./workflow end --summary "Workflow completion summary"
```
{% endif %}

